Class CTImage

java.lang.Object
  edu.harvard.lroc.eclipseplan.CTImage
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<CTImage>
public class CTImage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<CTImage>

Simple class encapsulating a CT image for translation to EGSnrc-compatible DICOM image. EGSnrc expects no metadata.

Version:
$Revision: 253 $
Author:

read

private void read()
           throws com.archimed.dicom.DicomException,
                  java.io.IOException
Reads in CT image data. Really, we are interested only in the image location, identified by DICOM tag (0x0020, 0x0032) named ImagePositionPatient.
